{projectIO.credits.table.bodyDesc}: Dedicated to Marcus Iunius Brutus Caepio
Performed by the Java Virtual Machine

Here’s to all the lawyers who rejoice us by dint of their writing and printing and scripture; those finest of people who uswards bestow the greatest of delights in virtue of their wonderous wisdom, which wretched creatures as thee and me may never fully fathom ourself.
Go now henceforth and forevermore recite thy verbiage which brings thee the most splendid of joys.
